      <title>劳氏下调全年业绩预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/lowe-s-lowers-full-year-guidance-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于房地产市场冻结，消费者不愿进行大宗购买和装修，包括自己动手的项目，因此劳氏公司下调了全年业绩预期。预计同店销售额将下降至少 3.5%。彭博情报的 Drew Reading 在“彭博未平仓合约”上谈论了前景。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/lowe-s-lowers-full-year-guidance-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:44:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将对中国特斯拉征收 9% 关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/eu-to-hit-tesla-s-from-china-with-9-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟周二表示，计划对从中国进口的特斯拉汽车征收 9% 的额外关税。这比其他制造商面临的关税要低。彭博社的 Abigail Doolittle 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/eu-to-hit-tesla-s-from-china-with-9-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 14:22:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
